  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Visit some of Slovenia's most impressive destinations on this popular multi-centre holiday</h2>
<p>Discover magnificent landscapes, dramatic scenery, and the varied flora &amp; fauna and wildlife of the Julian Alps. The majestic backdrops are formed by the jagged summits of Mount Triglav, <a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia’s</a> highest mountain (2,864 metres) and namesake of the country’s National Park which covers 880 sq. km. Nestled in this picturesque area are the intriguing destinations of <em>Lake Bohinj, Kranjska Gora and Bovec</em>: Fairy-tale <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a> enjoys one of the most picturesque and unspoiled natural settings at the foot of Mt Vogel. Take a day trip to <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a> who's beauty is renowned, nestled amidst dense pine forests and surrounded by the dramatic snow-capped Julian Alps - its famous tiny wooded island has become the national symbol of Slovenia. The small picturesque village of <a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a> sits at the confluence of the Sava Dolinka and Pišnica valleys against the dramatic backdrop of the Julian Alps. <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc8e45320754ead8a9f026b9de3f1ad" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc8e45320754ead8a9f026b9de3f1ad}" title="Bovec">Bovec</a> offers a fantastic array of activities in its idyllic valley which also was the setting for many scenes from the ‘Chronicles of Narnia’ film.</p>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options: </h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Ten nights in total with three nights in Bohinj and Bovec and four nights in Kranjska Gora</li>
<li>Travel on a Sunday - last departure around mid-September</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in Bohinj, between destinations and from your hotel in Kranjska Gora to the airport</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
