  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Bohinj</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/1c5894c85da24d24938effa0e8112f37" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1c5894c85da24d24938effa0e8112f37}" title="Hotel Bohinj">Hotel Bohinj</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106150/hotel_bohinj_lake_bohinj_outdoor_pool.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/3504abe3987e4750994b291df51440a5" /></p>
<p>The stylish Hotel Bohinj is just a few minutes' walk from the edge of Lake Bohinj, and is perfect for a romantic getaway. Picturesque walking trails are right on your doorstep, and after a day's adventure, you can relax in the spa or find a quiet spot in the garden with a good book. The food here is excellent too, and with a focus on sustainability, this hotel ticks all our boxes.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/03d8245538284121b5de9457ff5eb3be" href="/{localLink:umb://document/03d8245538284121b5de9457ff5eb3be}" title="Bohinj ECO Hotel">Bohinj ECO Hotel</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106151/bohinj_eco_hotel_lake_bohinj_wellness_area.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/345fdfe620ba4af9a18e9ad7502e1176" /></p>
<p>The Bohinj ECO Hotel is a great hotel with a central location in the village of Bohinjska Bistrica, around seven kilometres from Lake Bohinj. Inter-connected with the impressive Aquapark, it's a great spot for families with fantastic swimming facilities. Separate from the Aquapark, there's an adults-only spa with panoramic indoor pool.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Bohinj</a></p>
<h2>Hotel in Bovec</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/0b8f908a856e407dbbc84ecf4ed43b12" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0b8f908a856e407dbbc84ecf4ed43b12}" title="Hotel Alp">Hotel Alp</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106152/hotel_alp_bovec_exterior.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/1d88e3ee085a419fa50a07817afd3d00" /></p>
<p>Located in the centre of the beautiful village of Bovec, between the mountains and bright blue waters of the Soča River, is Hotel Alp. It’s modern and welcoming, perfectly situated for those that want to take full advantage of local sightseeing, hiking, cycling and exploring the stunning surroundings.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc8e45320754ead8a9f026b9de3f1ad" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc8e45320754ead8a9f026b9de3f1ad}" title="Bovec" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Bovec</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Bohinj</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba}" title="Hotel Kompas">Hotel Kompas</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106153/hotel_kompas_kranjska_gora_exterior.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/fc51937433504808bd2e4882609303b4" /></p>
<p>Hotel Kompas has a fantastic location on the edge of Kranjska Gora, with everything you need in close proximity. Generous buffet-style meals ensure you're well-fuelled for any adventure, and the swimming pool and spa facilities offer space to relax and unwind.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/4ed013e224da49958546ddb8415ef8af" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4ed013e224da49958546ddb8415ef8af}" title="Hotel Spik">Hotel Špik</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106154/hotel_spik_kranjska_gora_panoramic_view.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a736d3382b4a4b0fbca3a93a35b335dc" /></p>
<p>Hotel Špik is around five kilometres from Kranjska Gora, on the edge of the village of Gozd Martuljek. It has excellent facilities, with indoor swimming pools, spa and sports courts plus children's play area. There's easy access to plenty of great walking trails and it's a pleasant walk along the river to Kranjska Gora.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Kranjska Gora</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
